question: Siuànn-tiâu nn̂g-á ê lián-sû kó-thong ê lián-sû, ū nn̄g chióng? (nńg-á 1 n̂g-á 2)
2002 nî, 2003 nî, kap 2004 nî ê 'seng-seng chū chòe' (net loss as reported) lóng-chóng sī hō-chòe toā-só͘? (net loss as reported)
Uìnn-ê nî, 'chheng-chháu-su-chiah' kah 'chheng-chháu-su-chiah sū-si̍t' ê kó·-chiáⁿ jīⁿ-lō·-tōa-chiáⁿ bô-chha-pia̍h ê sûn-tōa chha-ê-sî, hit-ê sûn-tōa chha-ê-sî sī sím-mi̍h?
2002 ni kàu 2004 ni, kong-si ê "pro-forma net loss" ūi-hô chóaⁿ chóaⁿ?
answer: Tùi 2002 kàu 2004, chit ê kong-si ê "pro-forma net loss" chiap-chiap kiám-chhun kài tōa. Siúⁿ siáu-chha̍h tùi 2002 nî ê 1,201,666 hō͘ tō kiám kàu 2003 nî ê 354,400, koh kiám kàu 2004 nî ê 269,196, che piáu-bīn tī chit ê sî-kan lāi, hāu-lī ê chòe-chháu ū chin tōa ê chìn-pō͘.

question: 2003 ni 'add : stock-based employee compensation expense' chi 2077 ê sî, 'pro-forma net loss' sī siáⁿ-mi̍h?
2003 ni 'net loss as reported' tang 'total stock-based employee compensation expense' ê pài-pi sńg tōa củai?
Nā-sī 2002-nî ê 'stock-based employee compensation expense' kái-piàn sī 5,000, tō chiūⁿ-sī bô-tiāⁿ-miâ ê sò͘-jī ê-hoé, hit-nî ê tō-sǹg liáu-āu ê 'pro-forma net loss' ē sī siáⁿ-chē?
Koh chai liat, 'chuan-t’i k-lâi k-lâi cheng-lêng cheng-lêng' hām 'cū-sūan bô-chha-chí-chiok sió-chháu' tī 2002 chì 2004 nî ê chi-kan, ū siáⁿ-mih bīn-téng ê koan-hē?
answer: Bē-tàng khoàⁿ-chhut 'chuan-t’i k-lâi k-lâi cheng-lêng cheng-lêng' ê tōa-sè hām 'cū-sūan bô-chha-chí-chiok sió-chháu' ū chi̍t ê chiàⁿ-tùi ê koan-hē. Tī 2002 nî ê 38,126 gōa koh kàu 2004 nî ê 23,906 gōa, chha-chí-chiok sió-chháu ê cheng-lêng kiám-chó͘, chū-sūan bô-chha-chí-chiok sió-chháu iā liân-sòaⁿ kiám-chó͘ tùi 1,201,666 gōa kàu 269,196 gōa, che sī kóng, cheng-lêng sió-chháu-chha-chí-chiok ê nî chiah ū cheng-lêng ê chū-sūan bô-chha-chí-chiok sió-chháu.

question: In-mih chu-iàu ê siong-mu̍t ū siâu-mûi ê su-liāu tī peh-chhun ê nî-tō͘?
answer: add : stock-based employee compensation expense associated with modifications net of related tax effect included in net loss asreported

question: 2002 ni 'basic and diluted net loss per share as reported' ueng-ueng ke paí khì-lâi, ūi-siáⁿ?
answer: 2002 nî sī chiap-chiap ê gû-liâu. I ê 'basic and diluted net loss per share as reported' sī $-5.95, chhiau-kòe 3.8 pái tùi 2003 nî ê $-1.56 kap 2004 nî ê $-1.10. Chit ê sò͘-jī tī āu-lâi ê chiáⁿ-lâi ê kiam-chē piàn-tāng, hō͘ 2002 nî chiâⁿ-chòe chi̍t ê keh-siâⁿ-ê iâⁿ-lō͘ kiam-chē ê nî.
